Optional Libraries
------------------
  
   - To enable python support, use
	 1. Python (version 2.2+)		(http://www.python.org)
	 2. Boost python (version 1.30.2+)	(http://www.boost.org)


Basic Installation
------------------

       1) download CMake from our web site: http://ncmi.bcm.tmc.edu/ncmi/software/,
	  select 'EMAN', then select version "Compilation Libraries and External 
	  Software". Then download cmake.tar.gz.
	  
       2) install CMake:
	  % tar zxf cmake.tar.gz
	  % cd CMake
	  % ./configure && make && make install

       3) % cd EMAN/src; mkdir build; cd build
       4) % ccmake ../eman2
            make necessary changes here
	    Then type 'c', and type 'g'.
       5) % make
       6) % make install
